Package: dera.pq
Title: SEC DERA Data Sets as Local Parquet Files
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Ian D.", "Gow", email = "iandgow@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6243-8409"))
Author: Ian D. Gow [aut, cre] (ORCID:
    <https://orcid.org/0000-0002-6243-8409>)
Maintainer: Ian D. Gow <iandgow@gmail.com>
Description: Downloads SEC DERA Financial Statement Data Sets and Financial
    Statement and Notes Data Sets, converts the tab-delimited files in each zip
    archive to Parquet, and maintains update metadata in a local DATA_DIR-style
    data repository.
